name: realm
summary: The official Realm SDK for Flutter
description: Realm is a mobile database - an alternative to SQLite and key-value stores.

script_phases.name: Download Realm Flutter macOS Binaries
script_phases.script: source "$PROJECT_DIR/../Flutter/ephemeral/flutter_export_environment.sh" && cd "$FLUTTER_APPLICATION_PATH" && "$FLUTTER_ROOT/bin/dart" run realm install --target-os-type macos --flavor flutter

script_phases.name: Report Metrics
script_phases.script: source "$PROJECT_DIR/../Flutter/ephemeral/flutter_export_environment.sh" && cd "$FLUTTER_APPLICATION_PATH" && "$FLUTTER_ROOT/bin/dart" run realm metrics --flutter-root "$FLUTTER_ROOT" --target-os-type macos --target-os-version "$MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET"
